paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted variants in the BRCA2 gene, including clinical significance, penetrance data, and individual records.

functional_data.summary: The variant is a deletion leading to a frameshift.

variants.additional_notes: This variant was one of the most common mutations identified in the study.
key_quotes: the most common mutations were ERBB2 rs28933370 (p.N857S), PIK3CA rs121913279 (p.H1047L/R/P), and BRCA2 deletion (p.I605fs*9), impacting 46, 8, and 6 patients, respectively.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only one variant in BRCA2 was reported in the paper.
